          "reviewBody": "“Kolkata Model School provides an exceptional educational experience. The dedicated faculty ensures a nurturing environment for students to thrive academically and personally. The school’s commitment to holistic development is commendable, fostering creativity and critical thinking. With modern facilities and a well-rounded curriculum, KMS stands out as a premier institution in Kolkata. My child has flourished here, and I highly recommend it for its quality education and supportive community.”",
