          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very nice school with a good discipline and environment. The teachers are very helpful and cooperative. The students are encouraged to engage themselves both in academics as well as in various co-curricular activities, like chess, karate, and zumba. It is indeed a second home for the students.\nThe performances done by the students were very splendid and energetic. Kudos to both teaching and non-teaching staffs for their herculean efforts to make this annual function so grand and memorable.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Burdwan Model School - Purba Barisha"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Salome Singh"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-11-25",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter is a student at Kolkata Model School and I would highly recommend this school to parents who are considering to admit their children in the coming session. This school is on the verge of receiving affiliation from the CISCE Board hence their effort on the students is noteworthy. Their range of co-curricular activities are commendable as well. These provide the children to get a scope at mental refreshment and rejuvenate their creative aspect which is very important for wholesome development of the children. Overall it is my personal thought that only big school name is not sufficient to build children.... cooperative parents, good teachers and children friendly environment is an absolute necessity. I thank this school and it's administration for providing the first step to my daughter in building herself. Love Kolkata Model School.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
